  "translations": {
    "en": {
      "description": {
        "text": "One classic problem, some lines still to be done, and a few more good problems with quick access from Brommaplan. Not everything is fully documented, and some problems may need a session with a wire brush, but it is well worth an evening.\n\n=Directions=\nThere is a small long-stay car park behind the OK petrol station at Brommaplan. Park there and head into the woods on the other side of the footpath. Follow the path for just under 100 m; the first wall appears on the right.\n\n=Topo=\n\n=Problems=\n(A) The wall\n(B) Boulder 1\n(C) Boulder 2\nThere are one or more undocumented problems here.\n(D) Boulder 3\nA short distance further on, past boulder (C).",
        "method": "llm",
        "model": "gpt-5.6-sol",
        "sourceIds": [
          "legacy:brommablocken"
        ]
      },
